              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hello."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Yanes",
                  "text": "Hello."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "How are you doing?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Yanes",
                  "text": "Meh, I don't want to talk about it."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Oh ummm... fair enough. Goodbye."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Yanes",
                  "text": "Not too well. I miss my friend. She couldn't join us here today."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Why couldn't she join you?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Yanes",
                  "text": "She had some afterlife business to take care of. Nieve's always so busy."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Nieve? I used to know a Nieve, but she died during horrible circumstances."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Yanes",
                  "text": "Really? You must be [player name]! She talks about you a lot."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Does she? I miss her. Steve is alright, but... he's not Nieve."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Anyway, please send her my regards and let her know that I avenged her death."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Yanes",
                  "text": "I will."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
